title: Freshology, Inc. Recalls Chicken Salad Products Due to Misbranding and Undeclared Allergen
summary: WASHINGTON, March 22, 2016 Freshology, Inc., a Burbank, Calif. establishment, is recalling approximately 111 pounds of ready-to-eat chicken salad products due to misbranding and an undeclared allergen, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today.
